The core idea

Every result card in SmartIOC should have the same three layers:

FAST SUMMARY (always visible)
The “Tor/VPN/Hosting/Abuse/Geo” style stuff you described.

EVIDENCE (expandable, still human)
Short bullets with source names, and flags for conflicts.

RAW DATA (collapsible)
Full JSON dump for deep dive.

This keeps SmartIOC fast, but still trustworthy.

