How we implement this cleanly (without rewriting everything)

We add a single normalization layer in src/lib/iocAnalysis.ts:

New functions

summarizeIp(raw: any): IpSummary

summarizeUrl(raw: any): UrlSummary

summarizeHash(raw: any): HashSummary

Each returns a small normalized object like:

type IpSummary = {
  tor: boolean
  vpn: { isVpn: boolean; provider?: string; confidence?: number }
  proxy: boolean
  hosting: boolean
  abuse?: { score?: number; reports?: number }
  spamhaus?: { listed: boolean; lists: string[] }
  asn?: { asn?: string; org?: string }
  geo?: { country?: string; region?: string; city?: string; conflicts?: string[] }
}